IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. SIZEERR.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    ADD WS-A WS-B TO WS-C ROUNDED WS-D
        ON SIZE ERROR
            DISPLAY "overflow"
        NOT ON SIZE ERROR
            DISPLAY "ok"
    END-ADD.
    DIVIDE WS-A INTO WS-B GIVING WS-C ROUNDED WS-D REMAINDER WS-E.
    COMPUTE WS-X ROUNDED WS-Y = WS-A + WS-B
        ON SIZE ERROR
            MOVE 0 TO WS-X
    END-COMPUTE.
    SUBTRACT WS-A FROM WS-B ON SIZE ERROR DISPLAY "underflow".
    STOP RUN.
